					&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</description><author>羊城晚报</author><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 11:13:08 GMT</pubDate><enclosure url="" length="10000" type="image/png"></enclosure><guid isPermaLink="true">CBMiY0FVX3lxTE11UG5Uek9Iemh2NWFlMVpnUmIxRmZOZkVkNUlYN3hkTXRaOVhLMEtQeXN0MkZBVC0xSEkxTFg3NGc2REh0ckhOVUxvYTFXNGRkYmlNUE9NVndNeUVEVThZSjA0TQ</guid></item></channel></rss>